Interface INumericalValueSpecification

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity, IValueSpecification

    public interface INumericalValueSpecification
extends IEntity, IValueSpecification
    INumericalValueSpecification: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    A numerical ValueSpecification which is intended to be assigned to a Primitive data element. Note that the numerical value is a variant, it can be computed by a formula.
